items.title: Can J&J's Innovative Medicines Unit Sustain Growth Amid Stelara LOE?
items.description: JNJ's Innovative Medicines unit shows a growth trend, defying Stelara LOE and the negative impact of the Part D redesign.

items.title: J&J reports results from antibody combo trial for MM patients
items.description: The investigational combo resulted in an ORR of 78.9%, with over half of the subjects achieving a complete response or better.
